Review Body:
if you order and they are unable to provide a driver with paypal they take £1 out of your account, it takes upto 1month to be returned, do it numerous times you might feel yourself serious out of pocket,

i’ll see if they refund my money which is a bit more than a quid

be wary

booked a cab for a hospital appointment the night before for the morning and agreed time and price, with minutes to spare from booking time, they cancelled the cab and had to rebook and pay £10 extra!!! couldn't really refuse as it was too short notice to rearrange with a reliable cab company and i also had no physical cash on me and i couldn't rearrange the appointment.

contacted their customer services and was told that they do this to encourage the drivers to take the less popular jobs!!! (wtaf???!!!) no apology, no nothing!!

well uber fu, i won't be using you again and your uber eats 'service is just as c*ap too!!;
